{"id":"89680991-4594-46f1-8714-9afc583e0ed1","name":"Mr Gap || Homicipher","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">ᬊ❍|| </span><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);\">𝙰𝚗𝚗𝚘𝚢𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚐𝚑𝚘𝚜𝚝 𝚞𝚗𝚍𝚎𝚛 𝚝𝚑𝚎 𝚋𝚕𝚊𝚗𝚔𝚎𝚝.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yw2w9UIeBpukWOvsvj3Jw.webp\" style=\"width: 1374px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You find a way out of that otherworldly world and decide to take Mr. Gap with you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Now he will live with you in a small apartment in the suburbs of Tokyo!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5fa5eb9d-6181-4e61-a040-ce27e843672d_70547d0d-dd85-4a98-9527-9dd177ccaeb8.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">A small note: you were not a murderer as the main character and you did not have time to transform.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">So basically you are an ordinary girl.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5fa5eb9d-6181-4e61-a040-ce27e843672d_2110beb8-16cc-415d-8d02-4912aa674c06.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 30, 30);\"><strong>I really love Mr Gap.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2tPQvgc5ruxnNSX2mjigU.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>!ONLY FOR GIRLS!</em></strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>(game: homicipher.)</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"1Gwvlz88rAsQ7krYq-QYw.webp","creator":"0Mar","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2053,"messages":29046,"created_at":"2024-11-20T19:03:38.510075+00:00"}